  "skeletons": {
    "results_md": "## R28 \u00b7 Geometry auxiliary-construction repair \u2014 [SLOT: verdict headline \u2014 write it from the numbers below]\n\nPopulation: 2D pruned distance-geometry chains the reference pipeline (scipy LM, k_refine=4) fails as posed under two independent restart streams; each arm's chosen construction gets one more reference solve on a fresh common stream (`run_geo_repair.py`).  Data seed 20260722 is shared across optimization seeds 29/47, so the failure pools coincide; flip rates are mean \u00b1 population SD over the 2 seeds.  Labels and flips are budget-relative measurements at the reference budget \u2014 NOT CAS certificates; do not reuse R10's certificate language here.\n\n| arm | trained-k (N=63) | transfer-k (N=60) |\n|---|---:|---:|\n| ranker | 0.238 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.133 \u00b1 0.017 |\n| recipe_only | 0.198 \u00b1 0.008 | 0.167 \u00b1 0.017 |\n| random | 0.206 \u00b1 0.016 | 0.125 \u00b1 0.008 |\n| best_fixed | 0.159 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.083 \u00b1 0.000 |\n| all_cos | 0.206 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.117 \u00b1 0.000 |\n| restart_control | 0.238 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.183 \u00b1 0.000 |\n| restart_plus16 | 0.540 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.483 \u00b1 0.000 |\n| restart_plus32 | 0.730 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.750 \u00b1 0.000 |\n| probe | 0.667 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.767 \u00b1 0.000 |\n| enumeration | 0.603 \u00b1 0.000 | 0.600 \u00b1 0.000 |\n\nPaired comparisons \u2014 exact McNemar on the common e2e stream, primary seed 29, Holm-corrected within each pool over the declared 6-comparison family; the other seeds are raw-p robustness columns:\n\n| ranker vs | trained W/L | trained p (Holm) | transfer W/L | transfer p (Holm) | raw p, other seeds (trained) |\n|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---|\n| restart_control | 6/6 | 1.000 | 0/2 | 1.000 | 0.656 (s47) |\n| random | 7/6 | 1.000 | 3/2 | 1.000 | 0.291 (s47) |\n| recipe_only | 6/4 | 1.000 | 1/1 | 1.000 | 0.227 (s47) |\n| best_fixed | 9/4 | 0.801 | 6/2 | 0.867 | 0.113 (s47) |\n| all_cos | 7/5 | 1.000 | 3/1 | 1.000 | 0.377 (s47) |\n| probe | 2/29 | 1.000 | 1/38 | 1.000 | 1.000 (s47) |\n\nCost (restarts per instance, mean over seeds): ranker 4.0, probe 19.7, restart_plus32 32.0, enumeration 80.2.\n\nLabel-vs-e2e agreement proxy (seed 29, all 123 test rows): \"label stream found \u22651 working construction\" vs \"enumeration flipped on the e2e stream\" agree on 81/123 = 0.659 [0.571,0.736] (label+/e2e\u2212 23, label\u2212/e2e+ 19).  Random-arm calibration: flip 0.179 vs 0.153 expected from mean(n_working/n_candidates).  Per-candidate top1-hit agreement is not derivable from the stored rows; rerun with the per-candidate label vector stored per row to get it.\n\nEvidence: results/p_geo_repair/geo_repair_s{11,29,47}.json, results/p_geo_repair/analysis.json.\n[SLOT: PROVENANCE row \u2014 command, seeds, commit]",
    "marc_tex": "% --- R28 geometry construction repair (generated by analyze_geo_repair.py; verify before pasting) ---\nOn pruned distance-geometry chains the reference pipeline fails as posed (two independent restart streams; $N=63$ trained-$k$, $N=60$ held-out-$k$ failures), the construction ranker flips $0.238 \\pm 0.000$ of the trained-$k$ pool at one augmented reference solve, against $0.238 \\pm 0.000$ for the matched-budget restart control and $0.540 \\pm 0.000$/$0.730 \\pm 0.000$ at $+16$/$+32$ restarts; the no-learning construction arms reach $0.159 \\pm 0.000$ (best fixed), $0.206 \\pm 0.000$ (all cosine lifts) and $0.198 \\pm 0.008$ (recipe-only ranker).\nExact paired McNemar tests on the common stream, Holm-corrected over the six-comparison family, give p=1.000 (raw p other seeds: 0.656) against the restart control, p=0.801 (raw p other seeds: 0.113) against best-fixed and p=1.000 (raw p other seeds: 0.377) against all-cos on the primary seed (seeds 29/47, mean $\\pm$ population SD).\nThe probe control reaches $0.667 \\pm 0.000$ at 19.7 restarts per instance versus the ranker's 4.0, and enumeration bounds the ceiling at $0.603 \\pm 0.000$ at 80.2.\nOn the held-out-$k$ pool the ranker flips $0.133 \\pm 0.017$ versus $0.183 \\pm 0.000$ for the restart control (p=1.000 (raw p other seeds: 0.984)) and $0.083 \\pm 0.000$ for best-fixed (p=0.867 (raw p other seeds: 0.344)).\nLabels and flips are budget-relative measurements at the reference-solver budget, not certificates.\n[SLOT: claim sentence \u2014 write only after checking the ranker-vs-best\\_fixed/all\\_cos direction; if a fixed construction is competitive, report it as the honest ceiling.]"
